node.statement: INTERPOLATION EQUALS HOMOGENEOUS RATIO: At q=1, the ratio F*_mu(x;q=1,t)/P*_lambda(x;q=1,t) equals f_mu(x;q=1,t)/P_lambda(x;q=1,t). Since F*_mu = f_mu + lower-order terms and P*_lambda = sum_mu F*_mu = P_lambda + lower-order terms, and both ratios sum to 1, the identity of ratios follows from the Hecke symmetrization relation.
